Iteration 9 - Error 0.0967289 - Cost 407.812



STEP 4. Optimal control and optimal state.

%approximate optimal control.
uopt=u;
%approximate optimal state.
yopt=y;


STEP 5. We plot optimal control and optimal state.

Optimal control.

